Octopilot Pipeline Tools (op)
Copyright 2024 Octopilot (https://octopilot.app)

This product includes software developed by Octopilot.

The `op` CLI is a Go implementation of the Octopilot build pipeline,
providing multi-architecture container builds via Cloud Native Buildpacks
and Skaffold, with SLSA attestation and a GitOps-native release workflow.

If you use or redistribute this software, this NOTICE file must be
included in full in any distribution, documentation, or derived work
(Apache License 2.0, Section 4(d)).

For documentation and usage, visit:
  https://octopilot.app

